===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|nl|dum|vri}}, from {{inh|nl|odt|frī}}, from {{inh|nl|gmw-pro|*frī}}, from {{inh|nl|gem-pro|*frijaz}}, which derives from {{der|nl|ine-pro|*preyH-||to be fond of}}. Related to {{m|nl|vrijen||to love}}, {{m|nl|vrijdag||friday}}, {{m|nl|vriend||friend}}, {{m|nl|vrouw||woman}}, and {{m|nl|vrede||peace}}.

